---
title: Garlic Butter Prawn Po'Boys & Herby Mayo with Cucumber Salad & Spiced Fries
description: Let’s go down to the South, specifically Louisiana for their famous Po'Boy sandwiches, but why travel for them when we can bring them straight to your table. Keeping to those Southern styles, add in some prawns and serve with a golden side of fries.
